<h2 id="the-beta-season">The ‚ÄúBeta‚Äù season.</h2>
<p>We started Season 00 with the initial release of 1.13 on a local server (AnonJr‚Äôs old <a href="https://www.dell.com/support/home/us/en/19/product-support/product/alienware-m17x-r4/manuals">Alienware M17x R4</a> for the curious) with the seed <em>-1872826417</em>. Mostly this season is about changing the way we work together in a more stream-friednly way (a little more space between builds, making sure we‚Äôre always chatting via Discord, etc.), getting our recording and streaming gear in order, and working through building channels on Twitch/Mixer/YouTube. Each member‚Äôs page has where to find each of us.</p>

<p>In late April 2019 we upgraded the server to one provided by <a href="https://cubedhost.com/">CubedHost</a> given the struggles the old M17x was having with 1.13 and the builds we were doing.</p>

<p>Up until we upgraded to 1.14.x we were using a few data packs and crafting recipes, mostly from <a href="https://vanillatweaks.net/">Vanilla Tweaks</a> and <a href="http://mc.voodoobeard.com/">VoodooBeard</a>:</p>

<ul>
