<p><a href="/members/anonjr/">AnonJr</a> was running a texture pack consisting of the 1.14 beta textures as they were released, and a few items from <a href="https://vanillatweaks.net/">Vanilla Tweaks</a>. Because of the custom textures needed for a couple items, it‚Äôs also set as the server texture pack.</p>

<p>Now that we‚Äôre on the 1.14.x series we slimmed the server texture pack, and switched everything over to offerings from Vanilla Tweaks. Here‚Äôs the links if you want to play along with our current server setup:</p>

